name: .MOM File Extension
summary: Learn about .MOM files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Data model created with Apple's Xcode development software; stores a Core Data model that is generated from a program's code; saved in an archived version of the NSManagedObjectModel format.

content: MOM files can be imported into Xcode Design Tools by selecting Design→Data Model→Import... from the Xcode menu bar.
